      <T n="text">0xF0652683<!--String: "Sims can study the art of Swordsmanship and use it to <b><font color='#199C2C'>Duel</font></b> other Sims! Start by purchasing a Sword at the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Blacksmith</font></b> in the Verdemar Neighbourhood of Ondarion, from a <b><font color='#199C2C'>computer</font></b>, or a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Practice Dummy</font></b>.\n\nSims can then increase their skill using the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Practice Dummy</font></b>, reading <b><font color='#199C2C'>Skill Books</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dueling for Fun</font></b> with other Sims.\n\nOnce they reach Level 2, they can even join a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Swordsmanship Tournament</font></b> from a Gazebo that can be found in any of the neighborhoods in Ondarion."--></T>
